definitions.definition: Being born alive , as are most mammals , some reptiles , and a few fish (as opposed to being laid as an egg and subsequently hatching , as do most birds and many other species).
labels: of an animal or animal species
definitions.label_groups: of an animal or animal species

definitions.definition: Arising from an embryo that develops from the outset (rather than from a true seed that then germinates ).
labels: of a plant or plant species
definitions.label_groups: of a plant or plant species
